"Set up key binding

" window control
nmap ;   4<C-W>+
nmap -   4<C-W>-
noremap L   <C-L>
nmap >   <C-W>>
nmap <   <C-W><
nmap <C-k>   <C-W>k
nmap <C-j>   <C-W>j
nmap <C-h>   <C-W>h
nmap <C-l>   <C-W>l
nmap <C-p>   <C-o>

"next/prev file
nmap <C-n>   :bn<CR>
nmap <C-p>   :bp<CR>

"next/prev quick fix
nmap <C-g><C-n>  :cn<CR>
nmap <C-g><C-p>  :cp<CR>

